org.eclipse.viatra.dse.designspace.api

Interface IState

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    State

    public interface IState
    Abstract representation of a model state in the design space exploration process. See IDesignSpace for explanation of the general concept.

      • getId

        java.lang.Object getId()
        Every state has a unique id that was generated by an IStateCoder. An attempt to add a different state to the design space with the same id will be ignored. See IDesignSpace.addState(ITransition, Object, java.util.Map) and IStateCoder.createStateCode() for more details.
        Returns:
        the id of the IState.
